incoming.page_description.text: Tohaina ngā kōrero ngaro ki tō mātou rōpū tautoko

incoming.feature_disabled_description.text: Kei te monokia tēnei āhuatanga i tēnei wā. Pā mai ki te tautoko mō te āwhina.

incoming.memo_placeholder.text: He whakamārama poto (hei tauira, Tono tautuhi kupuhipa anō)

incoming.memo_hint.text: Āwhina mātou ki te tuku i tō karere ki te tangata tika

incoming.recipient_aria_label.text: Kōwhiria he kaiwhiwhi mō tēnei mea huna

incoming.recipient_hint.text: Kōwhiria ko wai ka whiwhi i tēnei karere haumaru

incoming.no_recipients_available.text: Kāore he kaiwhiwhi e wātea ana

incoming.secret_content_placeholder.text: Whakapiri kōrero ngaro ki konei (kupuhipa, kī, me ērā atu)

incoming.secret_content_hint.text: Ka whakamunaina ēnei kōrero, kotahi noa te wā ka kitea

incoming.success_info_title.text: He aha te mea e pā mai ana?

incoming.success_info_description.text: Ka taea e te kaiwhiwhi te tiro i tēnei mea huna kotahi noa te wā. I muri i te tiro, ka mukua tūturu te mea huna.

incoming.tagline2.text: Kia tawhiti atu ngā kupuhipa me ngā raraunga tūmataiti i te īmēra me ngā rārangi kōrerorero

incoming.end_of_experience_suggestion.text: Tiakina tō rīhīti mō ō rēkōtanga.
